⍝ Drop.tc
⍝ ═══════

      ⎕IO←1

      ⍝ Precond: A simple scalar or vector integer; Z nonscalar
      ⍝ inv: ⍴Z ←→ 0⌈(⍴B)-|A
      ⍝ inv: ⍴⍴Z ←→ (⍴,A)⌈⍴⍴B
      B ← ⎕RVAL 2 (5 6) (,0 1 0 0 0)
      A ← 2∣⎕RVAL 1 (,2) (,0 1 0 0 0)       ⍝ drop 0..1 from each axis
      Z ← A↓B
      (⍴Z) ≡ 0⌈(⍴B)-|A
1
      (⍴⍴Z) ≡ (⍴,A)⌈⍴⍴B
1
